COMMAND+ D  : to select multiple same words
COMMAND + L : To Select entire line
Command + /
Shift + arrow(left,right) : select the text 
Command + arrow (left,right,top,bottom) : to move in estreme right,left,top,bottom
Command + shift + arrow(left,right) : to select entire line
Option + arrow(left,right) : to move word by word
Option + Shift +  arrow(left,right) : to select word one by one
Option + SHift + arrow(up,down) : copy the selected text beleow or above
Option + arrow(up,down)  : move line up and down
Command + P : switch between files
Command + P + P : switch between last two files
Tab to add automatic completion 